  <metadata>
    <name>Col du Galibier (France)</name>
    <desc>France · 18.1 km · +1245 m · 6.9% avg. A 2642 m Alpine giant above Valloire, often the Tour's roof and a gateway to the Galibier-Lautaret. Approximate geometry anchored at the real trailhead for indoor training, not the exact road.</desc>
